You do realize they have some high pixel count texture packs, right?  Yeah, still blocky, but things like the very old now Sphax packs were 1024/2048 tiles way back in the day when Tekkit was new.  A high res tex pack with RTX would probably look pretty damn good; but there have been addons that gave good lighting for years as well; so this isn't that big of an improvement to those either :p 



I mean, if you just play on console, you might not know any better.  But addons have made minecraft a lot better looking and a resource hog for what, a decade now?
